&lt;p&gt;You’ll join our Chargeback Investigations team, a front-line financial driver and data integrity gatekeeper for Signifyd. You will play a key role in minimizing losses, maximizing revenue, and mitigating fraud and chargeback risk for our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
